# Whitelist: ignore everything, then re-include only what the image needs.
# The Dockerfile COPYs just scripts/ and the test OGG, so nothing else
# (secrets, runtime data, git history) needs to enter the build context.
*

!scripts/
!Required_Weekly_Test_NOAA.ogg

# Drop caches/tests that slip in via the re-included scripts/ dir.
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
